Heps=3 #thickness of EPS
hw=1.6 #height of water
Hfill=0.610 #thickness of fill
gfill=20 #unit weight of fill
geps=250/1000 #unit weight of EPS
Weps=Heps*geps #weight of EPS
Wfill=Hfill*gfill #weigth of fill
Wpave=24*0.3 #weight of pavement
Bw=9.81*(hw) #bouyancy force one side flooding
FS=(Weps+Wfill+Wpave)/Bw
print('FS=',FS)
if FS > 1.2:
    print('Pass')
else:
    print('not pass')

#Desing the yiel of EPS
e_limit=50  #elastic limit of EPS Trial
DL_pave=0.2*24 #deadload pavement
DL_fill=Hfill*20 #deadload fill
DL_eps=geps*Heps #deadload EPS
LL_traffic=20 #AASHTO
load_onwheel=10 #rigid pavement from chart
if LL_traffic > load_onwheel:
    LL=LL_traffic
else:
    LL=load_onwheel
load=DL_pave+DL_fill+LL+DL_eps
FS=e_limit/load
print('FS=',FS)
if FS>1.2: print("pass")
else : print('not pass')
